FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">New monster AI</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial"> Well , i just finished reading new patch message and it made me a little bit upset, maybe i have missed something , so if anyone read patch message differently, please explain me my mistakes. <br>
